page.title: 10Smuggling illegal immigrants
page.content: It was dark as we came closer to the shore. We were smuggling illegal immigrants. We were on the look out for the coastgurds. We stopped the engines and rowed toward land. When we landed our boat on the shore we looked for some where to hide the illegal immigrants. We decided to hide them in Nanjzel house. As we climbed the rocks to the house we saw a Coastguards van. We ran to a near by cave with the immigrants. The Coastguards came to the cave where we were and caught two of us but they did not find the rest of us. The next day we went to the nearest town to get the immigrants onto a bus to London. When we got there we had to get past the police. We did it in the end. We got Â£500 from each immigrant. After that we went back to the boat and set sail again.
